# Superboost config repo — WHITELIST model.
# Ignore everything by default, then re-include only authored config.
# This guarantees session transcripts, logs, caches, and secrets never get committed.
/*

# --- Authored config worth versioning ---
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/settings.json
!/superboost-version.json
!/superboost-expertise-report.md
!/keybindings.json
!/hooks
!/commands
# NOTE: /agents is intentionally NOT versioned — those are project-specific
# subagents that reference internal projects, and this repo is public.
# Non-framework hooks (commercial-engine pipeline) are also kept local-only:
hooks/lumos-*
hooks/validate_report_data.py

# --- Belt-and-suspenders: never commit secrets/junk even inside whitelisted dirs ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/id_rsa*
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
